    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="操作系统"><a href="#操作系统" class="headerlink" title="操作系统"></a>操作系统</h1><h2 id="进程和线程"><a href="#进程和线程" class="headerlink" title="进程和线程"></a>进程和线程</h2><h3 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109191155712.png" alt="image-20201109191155712"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109191445584.png" alt="image-20201109191445584"></p><h3 id="通信"><a href="#通信" class="headerlink" title="通信"></a>通信</h3><h4 id="进程间通信"><a href="#进程间通信" class="headerlink" title="进程间通信"></a>进程间通信</h4><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109193110806.png" alt="image-20201109193110806"></p><h4 id="线程间通信"><a href="#线程间通信" class="headerlink" title="线程间通信"></a>线程间通信</h4><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109193150619.png" alt="image-20201109193150619"></p><h3 id="线程间同步方式"><a href="#线程间同步方式" class="headerlink" title="线程间同步方式"></a>线程间同步方式</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205204925.png" alt="image-20201109205204925"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205225767.png" alt="image-20201109205225767"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205338684.png" alt="image-20201109205338684"></p><h3 id="有进程后为什么需要线程"><a href="#有进程后为什么需要线程" class="headerlink" title="有进程后为什么需要线程"></a>有进程后为什么需要线程</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109202257244.png" alt="image-20201109202257244"></p><h3 id="单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？"><a href="#单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？" class="headerlink" title="单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？"></a>单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubuser