= 10; 在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？"></a>A* a = new A; a-&gt;i = 10; 在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117204030799.png" alt="image-20201117204030799"></p><h3 id="含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布"><a href="#含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布" class="headerlink" title="含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布"></a>含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117205025664.png" alt="image-20201117205025664"></p><h2 id="缺页中断"><a href="#缺页中断" class="headerlink" title="缺页中断"></a>缺页中断</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109195031920.png" alt="image-20201109195031920"> </p><h2 id="页表寻址"><a href="#页表寻址" class="headerlink" title="页表寻址"></a>页表寻址</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109201834535.png" alt="image-20201109201834535"></p><h2 id="OS缺页置换算法"><a href="#OS缺页置换算法" class="headerlink" title="OS缺页置换算法"></a>OS缺页置换算法</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205808449.png" alt="image-20201109205808449"></p><h2 id="fork和vfork的区别"><a href="#fork和vfork的区别" class="headerlink" title="fork和vfork的区别"></a>fork和vfork的区别</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200021906.png" alt="image-20201109200021906"></p><h2 id="修改文件最大句柄数"><a href="#修改文件最大句柄数" class="headerlink" title="修改文件最大句柄数"></a>修改文件最大句柄数</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200413838.png" alt="image-20201109200413838"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200429238.png" alt="image-20201109200429238"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200455145.png" alt="image-20201109200455145"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
